          "settings": {
            "subheading": "<strong>Setting the Table for Marmont’s Grand Entrance</strong>"
          }
        },
        "text_hH6pWc": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Few dining destinations launch with as much buzz as <strong>Marmont</strong>, the latest addition to Crown Melbourne’s vibrant hospitality scene. Helmed by international hospitality maven <strong>Grant Smillie</strong>, this Californian-inspired venue blends sun-soaked West Coast charm with Melbourne’s signature culinary excellence. It’s an all-day affair, where patrons can transition from a casual lunch to sunset cocktails before immersing in a DJ-spun soundtrack that carries the night forward.</p><p>To match Marmont’s effortlessly refined aesthetic, Cedar Hospitality has delivered an exclusive collection of premium tabletop essentials:</p><p><strong>Steelite Blackline Slimline Platters, Plates, and Bowls</strong> – These aren’t just plates; they’re a statement. Hand-selected for their sleek, minimalist silhouette and renowned durability, the <strong>Blackline Slimline collection</strong> was chosen to ensure every dish at Marmont is plated with an understated sophistication. These pieces don’t just endure the rigours of high-end service; they elevate it, giving each dish a backdrop worthy of its artistry.</p><p>At Cedar, we know that branding doesn’t stop at the menu. That’s why we provided bespoke <strong>logo-printed crockery</strong>, reinforcing Marmont’s distinctive identity with every serve. From intricate plating to signature dishes, every touchpoint is an extension of the restaurant’s style and story.</p><p>A cocktail is only as good as the glass it’s poured into, and a steak deserves cutlery that feels just as refined. Cedar Hospitality supplied the polished details that complete Marmont’s immersive dining experience.</p><p>With an unwavering commitment to quality, functionality, and design, <strong>Cedar Hospitality is more than a supplier—we’re a partner in crafting Melbourne’s most talked-about dining spaces</strong>. As the go-to supplier for Crown Melbourne and leading venues nationwide, we’re proud to support Marmont as it redefines riverside dining, one perfectly plated dish at a time.</p><p> </p><p><strong>Marmont</strong><br/>Ground Level, River Walk/8 Whiteman St, Southbank VIC 3006<br/><a href=\"https://www.crownmelbourne.com.au/restaurants/marmont\"><strong>www.crownmelbourne.com.au/restaurants/marmont.AU</strong></a></p><p></p>",
            "text_size": "text-base",
            "text_line_limit": "none",
            "button_style": "btn--underline",
            "button_icon": "none"
          }
        }
